channel.title: Error on my server prompt when logging in
channel.description:
I'm trying to add stuff to my client file. I edit the java file, compile, and start server, but nothing takes effect. i figured its because i dont save the class file. So i tried that, and now the compile is file, run is fine, but when i log in my prompt gets this error message -
http://www.runescapetop.com/up/images/8ee6.png
I dont know what to do, because when it compiles its fine, when i run the server its fine, but as soon as i log in i get that. Can someone help?
